          "source_section": "<outputs>"
        }
      ],
      "redesign_guidance": "All artifact entries in <outputs> must include their full canonical path rooted at the tool directory (e.g., tools/agent-role-builder/role/<slug>-role.md for canonical, tools/agent-role-builder/runs/<run-id>/rounds/round-<n>.json for internal). The contract package_files values must match exactly."
