          "source_section": "<outputs>, <steps> Step 5, self-check issues"
        },
        {
          "id": "f2",
          "description": "The contract's package_files entries specify bare filenames (e.g. 'agent-role-builder-role.md') with no directory component, which is consistent with the markdown but equally incomplete. An executing agent cannot reliably determine the promotion target from either artifact.",
          "source_section": "Contract summary: package_files"
        }
      ],
      "redesign_guidance": "Add a canonical_directory field to the contract (e.g. 'tools/agent-role-builder/role/') and qualify all canonical artifact paths in <outputs> as '<canonical_directory>/<slug>-*.* -- Canonical: ...' so the self-check and any executing agent have an unambiguous promotion target."
    },
