          "source_section": "<scope> Not in scope"
        }
      ],
      "redesign_guidance": "Remove the duplicate bullet. Move the board-review in-scope clarification to the 'Use when' list or to <authority> Owns, and keep the out-of-scope entry a clean exclusion statement."
